channel.title: PI based server, Creating a commands list
channel.description:
Hello,
I have recently moved onto a new based server, and ive converted a commands list from delta to project insaity. Im having a problem with one part though. When i get to the end of the list, the list keeps going and says qj1 etc. In delta you would flushout the system. But im not sure what i would put to stop that from happeneing on a PI based server.
Help me please
Thank you for reading
